"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-team-gb-paris-olympics-b1172113.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  British athletes reconvened at their Parisian holding camp today in preparation for the Olympics, which get under way this Friday.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9975873136125427, \"rank\": 0.002281820747063512, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 64 track and field athletes are due to compete at the Games - and predominantly with a clean bill of health, following the final warm-up event for Paris 2024, theDiamond Leaguein London at the weekend.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6843873470131464e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.154118759922722e-13, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While many of the team's star turns opted to stay away from the event, the likes ofMatt Hudson-Smith,Keely Hodgkinson,Dina Asher-SmithandKatarina Johnson-Thompsonall opted to compete in the capital one last time.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One question mark remains over Johnson-Thompson, who recorded a best of 6.54metres in the long jump on Saturday in front of a 60,000-strong crowd, the exact same distance she managed in winning a second world title in Budapest last summer.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9998647319030544, \"rank\": 0.00013528639691441646, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She pulled out midway through the European Championships earlier this summer and had a series of injections in her Achilles in the aftermath, but said the problem seemed \\\"to have settled down now\\\".\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0958992927261665e-17, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.725149929785893e-11, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her recent form is promising.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She ran her best 200m since 2019 at the Olympic trials and managed a season's best in the shot put at a meet in Loughborough recently.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.5539286898674606, \"rank\": 0.6420185669702492, \"text\": \"Loughborough\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the rigours of seven events in the heptathlon are a different matter, but she said: \\\"I think I am in good shape.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the signs are there that I am coming into shape.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all I can ask for.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just praying I can take that into the heptathlon.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really happy with being able to get into the 6.50s [in the long jump] straight away, because it was an event I had not done since Budapest.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9998647319030544, \"rank\": 0.00013528639691441646, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tendinitis is an ongoing thing.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think a lot of people struggle with it.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes and goes, it gets bad and good again, so it's something I have to keep an eye on, but it's something I have got on top of now.\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you cannot predict a heptathlon.\\\"\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Question marks will remain about Johnson-Thompson's ability to go for multi-event gold, in contrast to Hodgkinson and Hudson-Smith, who have marked themselves as golden favourites in the 800m and 400m respectively.\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2168, \"end\": 2178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.985456526418413, \"rank\": 0.014758107731705243, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the capital, Hodgkinson broke her British record and set a world-leading time of 1min 54.61sec to win the 800m from Jemma Reekie and Georgia Bell, who both set personal bests in taking second and third respectively.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.985456526418413, \"rank\": 0.014758107731705243, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2318, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.365345337368467e-14, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemma_Reekie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jemma Reekie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemma_Reekie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemma_Reekie\"}, {\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"score\": 0.5951168371693653, \"rank\": 0.3611220076213676, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions  Winter escapes and activities to end the year in style  Hudson-Smith dramatically lowered his 400m European record to 43.74sec - and later insisted he had held back in the dying stages of that race.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2802, \"end\": 2817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.055732818099807e-19, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson was already looking to Jarmila Kratochvilova's 41-year-old world record of 1:53.28.\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2903, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.985456526418413, \"rank\": 0.014758107731705243, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2937, \"end\": 2958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jarmila_Kratochv\\u00edlov\\u00e1\", \"score\": 0.9999999963824848, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jarmila Kratochvilova\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jarmila_Kratochv\\u00edlov\\u00e1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jarmila_Kratochv\\u00edlov\\u00e1\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Briton said: \\\"We are getting closer.\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Briton\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q25379\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do I think it's beatable?\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, I would say 'yes'.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would take a very special race.\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully, I will have a long time to try.\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am feeling really good and confident ahead of Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3217, \"end\": 3222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.197963895961634e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hudson-Smith headed to Paris making his new rapid time for one lap of the track seem like little more than a box-ticking exercise.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.197963895961634e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's exactly what me and my team were aiming for, to get the world lead in time for Paris,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3445, \"end\": 3450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.197963895961634e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wrote 43.70 on a piece of paper before I left.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew at 370m I had it in the bag, so I eased down.\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got plenty more.\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a long time coming and I am actually healthy.\\\"\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 4520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3702, \"end\": 3711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9919239415910882, \"rank\": 0.008099458937703474, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3802, \"end\": 3811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9919239415910882, \"rank\": 0.008099458937703474, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3880, \"end\": 3888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"score\": 0.9999999763363124, \"rank\": 2.3659551195952656e-08, \"text\": \"Brighton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\"}, {\"begin\": 3946, \"end\": 3960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.717865731718098e-14, \"text\"